00:38:26.133 --> 00:38:29.967
and then just going up the scale
not counting the chromatic notes,

00:38:29.967 --> 00:38:33.033
so going up the scale one, two,
three, four, five, six, seven.

00:38:33.033 --> 00:38:37.800
